item.title: CVE-2019-10357|2024-08-04T22:17:20.501Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20pipeline%3A%20shared%20groovy%20libraries%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Pipeline: Shared Groovy Libraries Plugin 2.14 and earlier allowed users with Overall/Read access to obtain limited information about the content of SCM repositories referenced by global libraries.
